trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapServerType"></xref> class represents the type on which the XML Web service is based.
Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapServerType"></xref> class.
The <xref href="System.Type"></xref> on which this XML Web service is based.
A <xref href="System.Web.Services.Configuration.WebServiceProtocols"></xref> value that specifies the transmission protocols that are used to decrypt data sent in the XML Web service request.
Returns the duplicate <xref href="System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapServerMethod"></xref> associated with the specified key.
The key associated with the desired duplicate <xref href="System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapServerMethod"></xref>.
The duplicate <xref href="System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapServerMethod"></xref> associated with the specified key.
Returns the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapServerMethod"></xref> associated with the specified key.
The key associated with the desired <xref href="System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapServerMethod"></xref>.
The <xref href="System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapServerMethod"></xref> associated with the specified key.
Returns a <xref href="System.Boolean"></xref> that indicates whether SOAP data transmissions sent to and from this XML Web service are encoded by default.
`true` if SOAP data transmissions sent to and from this XML Web service are encoded by default; otherwise, `false`.
Gets a <xref href="System.String"></xref> that contains the namespace to which this XML Web service belongs.
A <xref href="System.String"></xref> that contains the namespace to which this XML Web service belongs.
Returns a <xref href="System.Boolean"></xref> that indicates whether SOAP messages that are routed to this XML Web service are routed based on the `SOAPAction` HTTP header.
`true` if SOAP messages that are routed to this XML Web service are routed based on the `SOAPAction` HTTP header; otherwise, `false`.
